# 统一文本文件的换行，避免 Windows/macOS/Linux 互相污染 diff
* text=auto

# 明确常见源码为文本
*.cs text
*.axaml text
*.xaml text
*.json text
*.xml text
*.md text
*.sql text
*.yml text
*.yaml text

# 二进制文件：禁止当文本 diff（避免乱码/巨大 diff）
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
*.7z binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.pdb binary
*.onnx binary
